<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>CSS Assignment</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>

<body>

<h1 id="mainTitle">Welcome to My Website</h1>
<h2 class="subtitle">About Cooking</h2>
<h3 class="section">Healthy Recipes</h3>
<h4 class="smallTitle">Quick Meals</h4>

<p class="p1">Cooking at home helps you eat healthy.</p>
<p class="p2">Fresh ingredients make food taste better.</p>
<p class="p3">Learning recipes improves your cooking skills.</p>
<p id="p4">Cooking can also be a fun hobby.</p>
<p id="p5">Families enjoy meals together.</p>
<p id="p6">Practice makes perfect in the kitchen.</p>

</body>
